SUMMARY:Wellness Walk (CANCELED DUE TO WEATHER)
DTSTAMP:20260616T174855Z
DTSTART:20260616T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:THIS EVENT HAS BEEN CANCELED DUE TO THE WEATHER. \nJoin Laura C
	onely of Urban Paths for a fun evening as we explore the trails and beauty
	 of Hermann Park on a guided 3-mile experience. All are invited to this co
	nversationally paced walk\; friendly pups on leash are welcome too! \nThis
	 event is free\, but registration is required and space is limited. Sign u
	p HERE. Participants will meet outside the McGovern Centennial Gardens\, l
	ocated at 1500 Hermann Drive\, with parking available in adjacent Lot C. \
	nLaura Conely is the founder of Urban Paths\, a walking wellness company. 
	As a certified teacher and coach\, she leads guided Wellness Walks that br
	ing individuals of all ages and fitness levels together to experience the 
	profound health benefits of: Nature\, Art\, Movement\, and Connection.\n\n
	https://hermannpark.org/event/wellness-walk-7/\n\nFrom Hermann Park Conser
	vancy
URL:https://hermannpark.org/event/wellness-walk-7/
LOCATION:McGovern Centennial Gardens\, 1500 Hermann Drive\, Houston\, TX\, 
	77004\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:hermann-park
CATEGORIES:Hermann Park Conservancy
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
